    <item>
      <title>美国邮政服务暂停接收来自中国和香港的包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-suspends-inbound-parcels-from-china-hk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政服务暂时停止接收来自中国和香港邮政的入境国际包裹，这可能会延误或阻止 Shein 和 PDD Holdings Inc. 的 Temu 等零售商的发货。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-suspends-inbound-parcels-from-china-hk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 02:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦迪被确认为特朗普的司法部长，领导司法部改组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/bondi-confirmed-as-trump-s-attorney-general-to-lead-doj-shake-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二晚间，美国参议院批准帕姆·邦迪出任唐纳德·特朗普政府司法部部长，让她接管一个庞大的机构，该机构对于特朗普政府在反垄断、移民和打击白领犯罪方面的工作至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/bondi-confirmed-as-trump-s-attorney-general-to-lead-doj-shake-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>历史性减税后莫迪面临首次重大选举考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/modi-faces-first-major-electoral-test-after-historic-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度首都周三举行地方选举，这对总理纳伦德拉·莫迪来说是一次至关重要的考验，十多年来，莫迪的政党一直未能从一个规模虽小但实力强大的竞争对手手中夺取德里的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/modi-faces-first-major-electoral-test-after-historic-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对内阁提名人的压力活动正在取得成效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-s-pressure-campaign-for-cabinet-nominees-is-paying-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 和塔尔西·加巴德 (Tulsi Gabbard) 于周二通过了参议院的关键审核，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 内阁的几乎所有提名人选都将得到确认，这是总统对共和党同僚的影响力的最新体现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-s-pressure-campaign-for-cabinet-nominees-is-paying-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:02:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚电视内阁会议陷入争吵和泪水</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/televised-colombian-cabinet-meeting-descends-into-rancor-tears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗 (Gustavo Petro) 的部长们互相指责，表达个人不满，导致首次电视内阁会议陷入激烈争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/televised-colombian-cabinet-meeting-descends-into-rancor-tears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马领导人因资产太过珍贵而无法割让，成为特朗普的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/an-asset-too-precious-to-cede-makes-panama-leader-a-trump-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马总统何塞·劳尔·穆利诺已经做了很多事情来安抚即将上任的美国总统。他已经限制移民路线，并宣布巴拿马成为美国新的南部边境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/an-asset-too-precious-to-cede-makes-panama-leader-a-trump-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 00:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称美国可能接管加沙，将难民送往其他地方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-insists-that-jordan-and-egypt-will-take-in-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在与以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡举行的新闻发布会上提议美国接管加沙地带，并承担重建这片饱受战争蹂躏的领土的责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-insists-that-jordan-and-egypt-will-take-in-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 21:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财政部从马斯克的 DOGE 团队中吸纳两名成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/us-treasury-brings-in-two-members-from-musk-s-doge-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国财政部已引进至少两名与所谓的政府效率部有关的人员：云软件集团公司 (Cloud Software Group Inc.) 首席执行官汤姆·克劳斯 (Tom Krause) 和曾在 SpaceX 和社交媒体平台 X 工作的工程师马尔科·埃莱兹 (Marko Elez)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/us-treasury-brings-in-two-members-from-musk-s-doge-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 17:16:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马考虑取消与香港亿万富翁公司的港口交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/panama-said-to-mull-canceling-port-deal-with-hong-kong-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴拿马正在考虑是否取消与运营巴拿马运河附近港口的香港公司的合同，此举可能是为了化解唐纳德·特朗普总统关于对抗中国在这条关键水道周围影响力的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/panama-said-to-mull-canceling-port-deal-with-hong-kong-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
